00:38:24,400 --> 00:38:33,199
[SPEAKER_00] Petar ga, Isus ga tri put ponovno pita, Petar Sinje Šimunov, ljubiš li me, ljubiš li me, ljubiš li me tri puta.

313
00:38:34,000 --> 00:38:35,679
